{"tid":700189,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷公投，美斯獲最佳球員獎","createTime":"2018-06-13T07:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T14:42:42.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"626a59ed880269e20240ad03e2759f8af43b8708","tid":700189,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"在法國雜誌《Onze Mondial(世界11人)》的評選中，巴薩球星美斯捧走了17/18賽季該雜誌的金球獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/0D/E9/ChOxM1sgkR-AV3pSAACDAOgqxtM427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F0D%2FE9%2FChOxM1sgkR-AV3pSAACDAOgqxtM427.jpg&h=1a803bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《世界11人》的金球獎評選始於1976年，由球迷投票評出當賽季最佳球員。美斯曾在2009、2011和2012年奪得該獎。在今年的評比中，美斯的得票率為28.6%，力壓利物浦前鋒沙拿的26.3%。皇馬球星C朗以18.1%的得票率位居第三。<br />\n<br />\n美斯在Instagram上曬出獎杯照，表示：&ldquo;謝謝《世界11人》的所有讀者。我非常自豪得到這座獎杯。我要藉此機會抱抱你們。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4a14e8d5399c2221fcc51fcf599f4a5bde0e88db","tid":700189,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T20:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a27bb476d35161dfbe6183337f5bd8e53a5e9ff","tid":700189,"uid":72454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T20:35:35.000Z","msg":"打完飛機未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0306d13f6b4ea28e21b9ba3649ad0b940faf56","tid":700189,"uid":153400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8819566d4fc6cdb39371a96b5d3e1a59b08af9","tid":700189,"uid":47303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"知啦知啦"},{"pid":"d20ad9cb3e3ab34ac8b47d88ae0bde4bfa1def1a","tid":700189,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"勁"}]}